## Devices Collection [/oems/:id/devices?limit=limit&include=includes]
Devices for a specific OEM can be accessed here.
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the OEM to perform action with. Has example value.
    + limit (optional, number, `1`) ... Numerical `limit` to apply to how many records are returned.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier`, `platform`, `oem`, or `all`

