## Device [/oems/:id/devices/:subid?include=includes]
Get a single Device object for a single OEM 
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the OEM to perform action with. Has example value.
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `subid` of the Device to perform action with. Has example value.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier`, `platform`, `oem`, or `all`

### Retrieve a Device for a given OEM [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                data: {
                  modified_by: null
                  name: "X"
                  is_phone: true 
                  is_tablet: false 
                  ppi: 9000
                  res_height: 720
                  res_width: 480
                  size: .5
                  platform_id: 2
